column5: Congrats on the so-far awesome year and officially becoming a pro!
Wow, lotsa real nice fish there. Congrats.  Nice looking new boat as well, though you might need a bigger truck, quite the squat on that Flex...
Great season so far and awesome ride! You will have many great years in that boat. Good luck this fall - I know there will be some Gbay giants sliming that Ranger soon...  Pete
